{"tid":1807580,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"繼續捉鬼呀, 遲早害死曬自己人","createTime":"2020-01-02T01:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T03:03:09.000Z","uid":69291,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3591319fc8c807b7c99ff974d3dbca9fb1a82561","tid":1807580,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T01:52:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你係做唔到野既唔該唔好懶醒<br />\n你根本唔識分人定鬼唔該你認<br />\n亂鳩咁捉害撚死曬自己手足<br />\n係呀<br />\n你地害撚死自己啲手足!<br />\n你幫班狗mark 曬人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做唔到唔該唔好懶醒<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n到時唔該唔好問前線去曬邊<br />\n有勇有和我地先行到今日<br />\n本身勇已經要受極大風險<br />\n依家仲要腹背受敵<br />\n畀你你出唔出呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a471696072d04524ade8dcc7f104907da861384","tid":1807580,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T01:53:57.000Z","msg":"本身諗住唔開post 講<br />\n但屌你聽完手足呻真係好撚燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b092dd18d319e46ab8f2b72e8a048aa36692c6","tid":1807580,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T01:54:56.000Z","msg":"隔撚咗成晚都係燥到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成撚日話手足唔係condom<br />\n屌你捉鬼直頭當手足唔係人"}